<div class="task">
  <div class="options">
    <label><input type="radio" name="q1"> Done</label>
    <label><input type="radio" name="q1"> Revisit</label>
  </div>
  <div class="task-title">1. Assign Static IP</div>
  Set the following on <b>clone-client</b> if your network is different please use your own subnet but set host 130:  
  <ul>
    <li>IP: 192.168.100.130</li>
    <li>Netmask: 255.255.255.0</li>
    <li>Gateway: 192.168.100.1</li>
    <li>NameServer: 192.168.100.1</li>
    <li>Hostname: servera.example.com</li>
  </ul>
</div>

