  <div class="task-title">9. Troubleshoot webserver</div>
  If successfully running, the webserver should show <b>"I am enjoying RHCSA preparation"</b> on port <b>82</b> without changing any configuration.
</div>

<div class="task">
  <div class="options">
    <label><input type="radio" name="q10"> Done</label>
    <label><input type="radio" name="q10"> Revisit</label>
  </div>
  <div class="task-title">10. Collaboration Directory</div>
  <ul>
    <li>Create directory <b>/project</b></li>
    <li>Full access to user and group, no access for others.</li>
    <li>New files inherit group ownership <b>developers</b>.</li>
    <li>Users cannot delete other user files.</li>
  </ul>
